<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.5">
<l>iṭariṉṟi yēyoru nāḷoru pōḻtilel lāvala kuṅkaḻiyap</l>
<l>paṭarpukaḻ pārttaṉum vaitika ṉumuṭa ṉēṟattiṇ ṭērkaṭavic</l>
<l>cuṭaroḷi yāyniṉṟa taṉṉuṭaic cōtiyil vaitikaṉ piḷḷaikaḷai</l>
<l>yuṭaloṭuṅ koṇṭukoṭut tavaṉaip paṟṟi yoṉṟun tuyarilaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Holding on to the one who gave, taking [them] along with [their] bodies, children,</l>
<l>the Veda expert in his own light who stood a glowing brightness,</l>
<l>driving the firm chariot so that Pārtha and the Veda expert rose,</l>
<l>while the whole world passed one time one day without affliction, I am without any sorrow.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
